# ========================================================================
# BlazeCommerce WordPress Plugin - Code Ownership & Review Requirements
# ========================================================================
#
# This file defines code ownership and review requirements for the
# BlazeCommerce WordPress Plugin repository. It ensures appropriate
# security review, quality assurance, and expertise-based code review.
#
# OWNERSHIP HIERARCHY:
# 1. Security-sensitive files require security team review
# 2. API integrations require both security and QA team review
# 3. Documentation requires QA team review
# 4. Workflow files require security team review
# 5. All other files default to QA team review
#
# TEAM ASSIGNMENTS:
# - @blaze-commerce/qa: Quality assurance and general code review
# - @blaze-commerce/dev: Development team for technical and security review
# - Combined teams provide comprehensive security oversight
#
# For more information about code ownership, see:
# https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositorys-settings-and-features/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners
#
# ========================================================================

