#
# REVIEW REQUIREMENTS SUMMARY:
# - Security-sensitive files: Dev team + QA team (dual review)
# - API integrations: Individual security lead + QA team
# - Workflows: Individual security lead + Dev team
# - Documentation: QA team (+ Individual security lead for security docs)
# - General code: QA team
# - Tests: QA team + Dev team
# - Security scanner: Dev team + QA team (enhanced team review)
#
# For questions about code ownership or to request changes to this file,
# please create an issue in this repository or contact the development team.
